ÜBUNGSZETTEL
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a project intending to provide a service for aggregating exercise sheets
at university and presenting them to users in a convinient way. It is written
for PHP ≥ 5.3 and, since I'm (the original author) enrolled at a German university,
most of the code is written in German. Feel free to translate it, if you want!

As for the code's

